1.0.0.name: kinglozzer/bfgoogleanalytics
1.0.0.description: A slimmed, trimmed & tweaked version of silverstripe-labs/silverstripe-googleanalytics. Designed for use in internal projects or where developers are the only CMS administrators; as users can break their analytics code by inserting invalid javascript.
